{"tid":981757,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix神劇《黑鏡》被書商告抄橋","createTime":"2019-01-14T14:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T14:12:55.000Z","uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"21204adb78678c20db92d5dc2ed92638bfbc384a","tid":981757,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T14:08:28.000Z","msg":"最近Netflix神劇《黑鏡》（Black Mirror）推出全新一集《黑鏡：潘達斯奈基》（Black Mirror: Bandersnatch），觀眾可以一邊睇劇一邊揀劇情同結局，不過最近呢條橋就被出版《Choose Your Own Adventure》系列嘅書商指抄橋，書商仲採取法律行動告Netflix。<br />\n書商指Netflix故意利用其書籍系列嘅品牌知名度嚟推出該節目。《Choose Your Own Adventure》系列於80至90年代，於年輕人中相當受歡迎，賣超過2.65億本書，據指其要求Netflix至少賠償2500萬美金（約港幣1.96億）。書商指Netflix曾經於過去幾年向其買版權，但最後唔成事，而家就擅自偷橋用，仲於劇中涉及殺人、吸毒、分屍等情節，對年輕人造成不良影響。而文件中亦透露，電影公司20th Century Fox最近就已向書商買版權去拍攝互動電影。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190113/59138429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190113%2F59138429&d=ku5Y7cvE3IkWa4GmX7CZ44S5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=fa1f867a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190113%2F59138429&h=c304b973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190113/59138429</a>"},{"pid":"92b8a37e40e7d658aad42e7d6dd2803a29a9a9d3","tid":981757,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T14:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfde7d7634216665da38f62b00fc2e36ccf05ef","tid":981757,"uid":58699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T14:12:55.000Z","msg":"咁普通都有得抄"}]}